msgid "Accessibility Inspector"
msgstr "Inspector de Accessibilitate"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.accessibilityinspector.metainfo.xml:12
msgid "Inspect your application accessibility tree"
msgstr "Inspecta arbore de accessibilitate de tu application"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.accessibilityinspector.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"Accessibility Inspector is as the name suggests an inspector for your "
"application accessibility tree. It lets you check all the items exposed via "
"At-SPI, too."
msgstr ""
"Inspector de Accessibilitate (Accessibility Inspector) es como le nomine "
"suggere un inspector per le arbore de accessibilitate de tu application.Illo "
"te permitte verificar anque le elementos exponite via At-SPI."

